{
  "text": "I didn't mean to get so far off the track of my original direction of questioning, but I think some of these excursions are very enlightening and will help in understanding of the basic mechanisms that we are so interested in in evolution. Ra stated that archetypes are helpful when used in a controlled way. Would you give me an example of what you mean by using an archetype in a controlled way? I am Ra. We speak with some regret in stating that this shall be our last query of length. There is substantial energy left but this instrument has distortions that rapidly approach the limit of our ability to maintain secure contact. The controlled use of the archetype is that which is done within the self for the polarization of the self and to the benefit of the self, if negatively polarized, or others, if positively polarized, upon the most subtle of levels. Keep in mind at all times that the archetypical mind is a portion of the deep mind and informs thought processes. When the archetype is translated without regard for magical propriety into the manifested daily actions of an individual the greatest distortions may take place and great infringement upon the free will of others is possible. This is more nearly acceptable to one negatively polarized. However, the more carefully polarized of negative mind/body/spirits will also prefer to work with a finely tuned instrument. May we ask if there are any brief queries before we leave this working? Should be mind/body/spirit complexes, presumably.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "I didn't mean to get so far off the track of my original direction of questioning, but I think some of these excursions are very enlightening and will help in understanding of the basic mechanisms that we are so interested in in evolution.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 239,
        "start": 1.6,
        "end": 37.783
      },
      {
        "segment": "Ra stated that archetypes are helpful when used in a controlled way.",
        "start_offset": 240,
        "end_offset": 308,
        "start": 37.923,
        "end": 44.383
      },
      {
        "segment": "Would you give me an example of what you mean by using an archetype in a controlled way?",
        "start_offset": 309,
        "end_offset": 397,
        "start": 47.884,
        "end": 53.324
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 398,
        "end_offset": 406,
        "start": 58.004,
        "end": 62.405
      },
      {
        "segment": "We speak with some regret in stating that this shall be our last query of length.",
        "start_offset": 407,
        "end_offset": 488,
        "start": 62.465,
        "end": 79.506
      },
      {
        "segment": "There is substantial energy left but this instrument has distortions that rapidly approach the limit of our ability to maintain secure contact.",
        "start_offset": 489,
        "end_offset": 632,
        "start": 81.966,
        "end": 115.409
      },
      {
        "segment": "The controlled use of the archetype is that which is done within the self for the polarization of the self and to the benefit of the self, if negatively polarized, or others, if positively polarized, upon the most subtle of levels.",
        "start_offset": 633,
        "end_offset": 864,
        "start": 119.289,
        "end": 164.472
      },
      {
        "segment": "Keep in mind at all times that the archetypical mind is a portion of the deep mind and informs thought processes.",
        "start_offset": 865,
        "end_offset": 978,
        "start": 166.632,
        "end": 187.534
      },
      {
        "segment": "When the archetype is translated without regard for magical propriety into the manifested daily actions of an individual the greatest distortions may take place and great infringement upon the free will of others is possible.",
        "start_offset": 979,
        "end_offset": 1204,
        "start": 189.554,
        "end": 237.738
      },
      {
        "segment": "This is more nearly acceptable to one negatively polarized.",
        "start_offset": 1205,
        "end_offset": 1264,
        "start": 239.538,
        "end": 250.598
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, the more carefully polarized of negative mind/body/spirits will also prefer to work with a finely tuned instrument.",
        "start_offset": 1265,
        "end_offset": 1389,
        "start": 252.219,
        "end": 277.74
      },
      {
        "segment": "May we ask if there are any brief queries before we leave this working?",
        "start_offset": 1390,
        "end_offset": 1461,
        "start": 280.721,
        "end": 291.822
      },
      {
